Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么今天的课就上到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在白昼的时间变短了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要在天黑之前回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  去玩吧  去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:12.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}去玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立马就把什么都称作plasma了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃车站前的那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  美绪也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已经先回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没回答就跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会不会对相生同学不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再稍微像普通的女孩子一点来打招呼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我叫东云名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个发条是…这个…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为附近的咖啡店重新翻修了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就试着进去看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式浓咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要Tea的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.46,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(400,00)\bord20\shad0\be20\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N64
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}以下出现的都是咖啡的术语，Tall代表标准杯。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式浓咖啡的Tall杯对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tall？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tall和透的发音相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T代表透？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我还在想喝份意式浓咖啡的Tea的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那么就给我意式浓咖啡的T的Small吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Short代表小杯，和Small差不多。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想点意式浓咖啡的Short吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我那个Small的Short杯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是意式浓咖啡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡有分热的和冰的两种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就给我热的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果是热的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小还有分…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Solo为单份浓缩，Doppio为双份浓缩。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Solo和Doppio两种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DoDoDoDoDo…Doppio！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio又是什么鬼东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio…Doppio
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio到底是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,230)}今日的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  我差点忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想点这个今日的咖啡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的咖啡就是意式浓咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那您是要Solo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是Doppio的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio…Doppio…Doppio的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就请你帮我选个适合的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是您的意式浓咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还是去自动售货机买好了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:43.33,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,350)\fad(400,400)}投\N球\N接\N球\N练\N习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了棒球手套作为外孙小实的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公  我要丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像隔那么远的话是丢不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然外孙就是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  你就投个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是今天就向外孙展示一下我帅气的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sinker…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
