Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧了呢  笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么  发生什么了  事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小次郎  你在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像刚出生的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃饭吗  会冷掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美绪  真是的
