Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么今天的课就上到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考试的范围已经贴出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家各自确认一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃总是一放学就迅速跑回家呢
