Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一有机会的话  我就会想要不要装傻
