Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大工汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  能借我橡皮擦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  借我橡皮擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.50,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(400,400)\bord10\shad0\be30\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N66
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这个与其说是擦  倒不如说是拉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  借我橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣也没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜吧  哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow  不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则是一边一边地猜  刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那规则是什么时候定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就从麻衣开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧  请随便调查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好烫烫烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算不算  不能用攻击招数的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣要One pena呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One pena是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是One penalty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,335)\fs25}一次惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One penalty会发生什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请我喝23瓶果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还怀恨在心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  祐子  吃干脆面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观自在菩萨  行深般若波罗蜜多时  照下五…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}源自般若波罗密多心经
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险  差点就上套了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是照下五  是照见五
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为能行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要Two  pena了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了  我可不会把有东西的一边伸出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么祐子  把橡皮擦给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好  给  如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色橡皮擦  技能篇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然角色橡皮擦擦不干净呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃果然是个机器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃很讨厌这么说她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  为什么讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人不是很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跑出去吧
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.64,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,365)\fad(400,00)\bord10\shad0\be30\3c&HFFFFFF&}藏\N了\N15\N年\N的\N真\N相\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要戴这个上街吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢脸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这没志气的臭团子
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.91,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N67
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  东云  东云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  原来是研究所啊  好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  让你久等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎…怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么相生同学会来我们家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是  啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让她和博士撞见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机器人的事实就会暴露无遗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}咦  名乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}莫非你是名乃的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哇 进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下  也许她只是来送资料之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样  就在玄关…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  请不必张罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然进来了那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在博士胡说八道之前把事情办完…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子饿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫阪本的猫  会说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能有那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪…阪本先生  请学猫叫  喵一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么我现在要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵一个  阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  只是普通的猫对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  因为今天有客人在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有好好地打个招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相生祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是名乃的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我是博士  是我制造了名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你制造的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  这么小却这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就是博士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  相生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是亲戚的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她爸妈都要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚也回不了家  所以要我帮忙照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  对吧  呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我去重新泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名乃你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶的话  就按这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气啊  帅爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个是帅气语句对决
